title: Google's advertising tech targeted in European publishers' complaint - Reuters
content:

description: Google on Friday was targeted in an antitrust complaint by the European Publishers Council over its digital advertising business, potentially strengthening EU antitrust chief Margrethe Vestager's investigation into the issue.
